        <title>CENTER (CARRIER) BEARING</title>
        <para>Press the center bearing assembly and both slingers off the stub shaft (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0600116">Figure 16</hotlnk>). The center bearing is serviced as a complete assembly,
            therefore separating the "U" shape bracket from the rubber cushion is not required.
        </para>
